snippet.title: Knockbots Concept Trailer (WIP)
snippet.description:
Knockbots is a game i'm currently developing together with Lucas Gullbo (https://twitter.com/Noxlof)

it's an intense & action packed arena game, which focuses on multitasking and awareness!
